The PHP files in this directory simplify working with (Open)LieroX data in PHP.
Currently there are functions for the following tasks:
Get level info and create level image or level thumbnail
Get mod info and weapon list
Convert skin to animated gif
Extract one frame from a skin
Get serverlist from masterservers
Get server info about a (O)LX server
Get a fast info about a (O)LX server
Ping an (O)LX server

The functions are defined in lxutils.php. For examples see test.php.